GeneralExplanation.Identifier: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, line 11
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: The executive vice-president as well as a subcommittee of the board will review the Form 990 prior to filing. The Form 990 in summary will be shared with the board prior to filing.

GeneralExplanation.Identifier: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, line 12c
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: MJF Housing, Inc. does regularly and consistently monitor and enforce compliance with the conflict of interest policy. Specifically, each year all board members are provided a copy of the policy and a statement to complete, sign and return. A committee reviews the statements for any conflicts and addresses any conflicts.
